{"tid":712741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"矽谷夫婦fb眾籌　5日獲逾億元","createTime":"2018-06-22T10:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T11:08:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"41e5db79b4c1c8d0a01e60abe2d795fa32c01898","tid":712741,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:32:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180622/20427824\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180622%2F20427824&d=PuaKngDH%2FZM%2BerZQRb5l9f9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=c6e7e253\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180622%2F20427824&h=d1ebc528\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180622/20427824</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月22日 <br />\n<br />\n矽谷夫婦fb眾籌　5日獲逾億元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180622/large/22wk2p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180622%2Flarge%2F22wk2p.jpg&h=2f829318&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■紐約市有孩子高舉標語，指孩子屬於父母。路透社<br />\n<br />\n美國一對矽谷夫婦不忍當局將人蛇家庭骨肉分離，在facebook籌款1,500美元（11,700港元），希望幫助至少一個家庭，沒料到一呼百應，短短5日籌得近1,400萬美元（1.09億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n育有一名兩歲女兒的威爾納夫婦（David and Charlotte Willner）是fb前員工，上周六在fb設立「讓移民父母跟他們的孩子團聚」籌款活動。<br />\n<br />\n對於籌款成績遠超乎想像，他們前日透過發言人發表聲明說：「開始時只想幫一個家庭，結果發展成一個運動，可以幫到無數人。無分黨派，大家都為孩子在邊境要跟父母分離感到沮喪。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n提供法律援助<br />\n<br />\n逾33萬捐款者來自美國及世界各地，包括fb行政總裁朱克伯格及營運總裁桑德伯格。整筆善款會捐給非牟利的「難民及移民教育及法律服務中心」（RAICES），為骨肉分離的家庭及孩子提供法律援助。RAICES在fb留言指，善款數字反映「民眾是如何強烈反對這政府的殘忍政策」。<br />\n<br />\n即使特朗普前日簽署行政命令不再分離人蛇家庭，威爾納夫婦認為這不代表孩子可隨時回到家人身邊、孩子所受創傷得以痊癒，他們的援助工作會繼續。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/德新社  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n死忠支持者：特逼不得已執法<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n推「零容忍」獲總統贈筆　國土安全部長變過街老鼠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n妻女力諫　特朗普叫停偷渡客骨肉分離<br />\n<br />\n佐治古尼捐78萬　協助移民兒童<br />\n<br />\n死忠支持者：特逼不得已執法<br />\n<br />\n推「零容忍」獲總統贈筆國土安全部長變過街老鼠<br />\n<br />\n維珍尼亞州羈留中心爆醜聞少年人蛇控訴美邊防：我被脫光綁兩天半"},{"pid":"1125a68b30c075b8901da764a82e3afa67b0007f","tid":712741,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:33:57.000Z","msg":"1人1蚊"},{"pid":"43bc4655ba3ad5229b0575e056c586b05536dcae","tid":712741,"uid":60831,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:35:05.000Z","msg":"冇撚得救"},{"pid":"92210cbcbce512af65ae715f8005ce2a7003592e","tid":712741,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:35:39.000Z","msg":"筆錢凸左駛去邊"},{"pid":"bb7b349a0567b104f0f400615e1d5ca12cb9a1d9","tid":712741,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92210cbcbce512af65ae715f8005ce2a7003592e","tid":712741,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:35:39.000Z","msg":"筆錢凸左駛去邊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:36:46.000Z","msg":"行政費？"},{"pid":"d3b625266e3372ff6177325751bee2365e2de6f6","tid":712741,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb7b349a0567b104f0f400615e1d5ca12cb9a1d9","tid":712741,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92210cbcbce512af65ae715f8005ce2a7003592e","tid":712741,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:35:39.000Z","msg":"筆錢凸左駛去邊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:36:46.000Z","msg":"行政費？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:38:40.000Z","msg":"facebook fat fat la"},{"pid":"f7150e55ac234c1e1e80f2b9ac69578b0e5dd2df","tid":712741,"uid":18568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:38:58.000Z","msg":"Fat fat lu <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a519ca2b8fac80252b70b3b8be6418375bf82c99","tid":712741,"uid":60092,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018